Name: Eternal Space Battles
About the game: Eternal Space Battles is a classic wave-based side-scrolling shooter with bullet hell elements. - Storm into space battles against more than 20 types of enemies, plus challenging bosses. - Buy new ships and upgrade them to get to the top of the leaderboard. - Complete missions and advance through game levels to earn points and cash! - More than 50 Steam achievements of varying difficulty. Earth is under attack by alien invaders. The United Earth Forces' High Command has tasked 3 superior battle spaceships, equipped with the latest in human technology, with defeating the aliens' armada. Take control of your ship, and teach that alien scum a lesson! The fate of the universe rests in your hands!
